OL,3,CSunak says government prevented 'mass
OL,4,Cunemployment' during Covid pandemic
OL,6,FNot all jobs could be saved during the
OL,7,FCovid-19 pandemic but the government
OL,8,Fprevented "mass unemployment", Rishi
OL,9,FSunak has told the Covid inquiry.
OL,11,FThe former prime minister also said he
OL,12,Fwas advised by medical officials not
OL,13,Fto "go too early" with interventions
OL,14,Fat the start of the outbreak.
OL,16,FSunak, who was chancellor during the
OL,17,Fheight of the crisis, having stepped
OL,18,Finto the role in mid-February 2020,
OL,19,Fwas giving evidence to the UK Covid-19
OL,20,FInquiry.
