OL,3,CSunak says government prevented 'mass
OL,4,Cunemployment' during Covid pandemic
OL,6,FSunak said the government was
OL,7,F"successful in preventing mass
OL,8,Funemployment" and that the impact on
OL,9,Fjobs was "considerably better than
OL,10,Fwhat anyone had forecast at the early
OL,11,Fstages of the pandemic".
OL,13,FThe coronavirus job retention scheme,
OL,14,Fknown as furlough, was announced by
OL,15,FSunak in March 2020.
OL,17,FAround 11.7 million employee jobs were
OL,18,Ffurloughed through the scheme, which
OL,19,Fapplied from March 1 2020 to September
OL,20,F30 2021, and cost around #70 billion.
