OL,6,FThe inquiry has received "generally
OL,7,Fpositive evidence" about the impact of
OL,8,Fthe scheme, which mitigated against an
OL,9,F"increase in inequality because of its
OL,10,Fpreservation of jobs", counsel to the
OL,11,Finquiry Richard Wright KC said.
OL,13,FSunak said a more targeted version of
OL,14,Fthe furlough scheme was drawn up by
OL,15,Fthe government in 2020 but "never saw
OL,16,Fthe light of day" because of the
OL,17,Fnational lockdowns that followed.
