OL,6,F"I cared about trying to figure out if
OL,7,Fthere was a better way to do this ` is
OL,8,Fthere a more targeted way that would
OL,9,Fsave us money and help economic
OL,10,Factivity return," he told the inquiry,
OL,11,Fbut he concluded the benefits of such
OL,12,Fan alternative would not "outweigh the
OL,13,Fcosts".
OL,15,FSunak told the inquiry that the
OL,16,Finitial advice Treasury officials were
OL,17,Fgiven was not to intervene too early.
