OL,6,F"Two or three days after, it was
OL,7,Fdecided that wasn't going to be
OL,8,Fachievable, which is why we had to
OL,9,Fmove to a full mandatory lockdown."
OL,11,FA key finding from the Covid inquiry
OL,12,Flast month was that the government did
OL,13,Fnot take the virus seriously enough
OL,14,Funtil it was "too late", with February
OL,15,F2020 a "lost month" for action.
