OL,6,FSunak told the inquiry: "If this thing
OL,7,Fhappens again, it's not obvious to me
OL,8,Fthat there's some learning from that
OL,9,Fperiod that would make it easier for
OL,10,Fsomeone in my position to make that
OL,11,Fbalance."
OL,13,FOn the self-employed income support
OL,14,Fscheme, the former prime minister said
OL,15,Fthere were challenges with it, given
OL,16,Fthat those applying had to self-
OL,17,Fcertify.
OL,19,FBut he said it was right to support
OL,20,Fself-employed people and that he would
OL,21,F"do it again" if in the same position.
